This is container for tools we use for System Rescue CD.

Currently 3 packages available:
  bash < <(curl -L https://raw.github.com/doubledrones/system_rescue_cd_tools/master/install-chef.sh)
  bash < <(curl -L https://raw.github.com/doubledrones/system_rescue_cd_tools/master/install-sudo.sh)
  bash < <(curl -L https://raw.github.com/doubledrones/system_rescue_cd_tools/master/install-git.sh)


Tested on System Rescue CD 3.0.0 on 7.05.2013
